Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:05.40,TenshiOri_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1408,936)\fad(549,0)}第12話      「天使的目光」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:18.11,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,廣闊的天空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:26.50,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,天使與人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.99,0:00:31.30,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,人立於大地之上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:36.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,天使飛舞于空中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:45.10,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,天使們用愛把人們連結在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:49.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,新生的花兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:54.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,開滿全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.00,0:01:04.70,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這是天使與人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:47.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽見了聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:55.80,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那呼喚著我的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:02:09.84,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,不可思議的世界在等著我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:34.10,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,被萬丈光芒籠罩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:40.12,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界真是耀眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:47.49,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,它正在呼喚著我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:03:00.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,滿溢著溫和愛意的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:07.56,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這個美妙的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:18.35,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到天使的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:19.82,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我是蘇伊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:20.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我是蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:23.52,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 我記得你叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.55,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,對 阿內莫涅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:27.80,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,阿內莫涅？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.34,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我們給你帶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:32.06,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 阿內莫涅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:48.55,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這是個色彩斑斕 繁花似錦的美妙的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:51.14,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到天使的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.24,0:03:55.60,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,與朋友們一起笑口常開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:04:00.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,幸福地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.93,0:04:05.05,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次享受迎風的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:10.20,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次將這般色彩映入眼簾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:16.75,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次萌生出的這份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.92,0:04:24.20,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠將世界填滿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.75,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,天使的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:31.05,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,就只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:38.65,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,用弓箭將愛意送到人間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.64,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,美味的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.57,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,要來一份嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:04:59.52,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,曲奇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:00.38,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,馬卡龍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:01.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,紙杯蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:05.35,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,即將開張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.32,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我們兩人的店鋪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:13.85,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,讓這個街道上的大家嘗到這幸福的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:15.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,用這美味的甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:19.80,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好想有個美妙的邂逅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:23.47,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,黛西 別老想著戀愛了 快來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:26.26,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,卡露米婭有喜歡的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:28.06,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:30.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,正忙著店裡的活兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:31.30,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,別想了 快來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:32.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:43.17,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好想感受心動的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:48.85,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這羽毛真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:59.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,種子冒芽而出 然後開出花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:03.36,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是天使的心靈 也能萌生出愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.90,0:06:07.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,得為他人送去愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.33,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 阿內莫涅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:20.35,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,明明現在的天氣這麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:24.20,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊對啊 為什麼你好像很悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:25.83,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:32.84,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口會如此難受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:39.19,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,在見到那個人之後一直在想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:44.67,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,她現在到底在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:49.60,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這心中的激揚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:53.59,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好想見到她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:07:01.22,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,萌生出的這份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:08.58,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好想確認清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.95,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我來見你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.65,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,為了確認清楚我心中的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:16.82,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在想你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:18.89,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都很想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.55,0:07:23.16,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫黛西 請問你的名字是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.32,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,黛西 我叫阿內莫涅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:27.35,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.73,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,是以你的羽毛為主題製作的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.94,0:07:32.44,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 黛西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:36.79,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這個時候還在外邊的話會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.93,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫阿內莫涅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.17,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,銀蓮花？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.15,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,開花了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.22,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.04,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣 小心別感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.83,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:56.52,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,就算與身為天使的你結緣也會早早先去世
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.50,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.22,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,阿內莫涅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:07.95,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,卡露姆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:12.61,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那位人類少女並沒有接受你的愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.12,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是答案
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:16.33,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此我也想待在她的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:17.83,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,和黛西在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:21.43,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,和人類以愛意相連的唯一方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:23.42,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你成為人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:25.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,然後翻越時間的山峰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.20,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我能夠成為人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.02,0:08:32.05,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果即使你成為了人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.18,0:08:34.07,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那位少女還是沒有接受你的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:35.82,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,你就會消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:38.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此你還是想去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.03,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,就打開試煉的大門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:43.83,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,阿內莫涅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.95,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會阻止你的 雖然有點難過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.35,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這種形式的愛真是美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.51,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,卡露姆大人 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:57.16,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我清楚了 那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:25.52,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,在天亮之前翻過那座山 前往少女的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.48,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊上路 時間沒有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:29.80,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:44.80,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,踏著冷冰冰的雪地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:49.55,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,腳底傳來刺骨的疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.96,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,原來這就是寒冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:54.10,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我早已決定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:59.95,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,離開懷念而又溫柔的天使的國度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:08.37,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,只為前往你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:19.95,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我心中萌生的這感情已無法阻擋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:26.65,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼胸懷著希望前進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:34.78,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,前往你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:42.50,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,讓愛的花朵綻放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:49.66,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.35,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:54.36,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,黛西？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:56.20,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我是瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:59.75,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,黛西是我的奶奶 你是她的熟人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.20,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我是 我是阿內莫涅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:05.35,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來見黛西的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.11,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,阿內莫涅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:10.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你就是那個天使？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.95,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,非常遺憾…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:16.16,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶她已經
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.78,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,黛西她是什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.17,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,在我很小的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.88,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,她總是跟我講天使的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:35.48,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等我一會兒 我去拿點吃的東西過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.11,0:11:37.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.55,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明應該會消失才對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.73,0:11:51.73,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.58,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 這是我們店的招牌點心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:11:57.75,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:00.66,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶總是念叨著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:03.30,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有一天來了個天使一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:05.15,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,就給她嘗嘗這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:15.74,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,察覺到我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:24.30,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,萌生了對你的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:36.20,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這份想要傳達給你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:48.05,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,口口相傳的美麗天使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:53.85,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我憧憬著你這般 傳說中的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:57.53,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我們兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:01.49,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,相遇於此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:12.70,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,正是要將這種蛋糕傳承下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:21.09,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,直到生命的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:57.95,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次享受迎風的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:05.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次將這般色彩映入眼簾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.45,0:14:08.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次萌生出的這份愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:17.55,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠將世界填滿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:34.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,廣闊的天空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:43.65,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,天使與人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:48.35,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,人立於大地之上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:52.82,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,天使飛舞于空中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:15:01.80,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,天使們用愛把人們連結在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:06.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,新生的花兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:11.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,開滿全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:21.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是天使與人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.77,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:34.20,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,戲劇怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.34,0:15:35.80,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:38.05,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,服裝也很適合你們 真的很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:39.25,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼小花已經換下戲服了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:43.32,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這之後還要集體拍照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.76,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有那種安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:48.48,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 老師說過讓我們把宮姐帶過去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.63,0:15:51.44,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 不我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:54.08,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 別不情願了 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.59,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽代替我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:16:01.77,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我還要回鬼屋收拾打掃之類的 想都別想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:06.30,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下來也要回家收拾收拾準備睡覺 沒辦法去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:07.78,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,你閑還是你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:09.65,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.84,0:16:14.75,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼事啊 老師會對我發火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:19.50,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你這次幫我們製作服裝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:22.85,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,…不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,托你的福 戲劇順利落幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.47,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子們也留下了一段美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:29.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:33.21,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,真的謝謝你了 宮姐小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:34.15,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:39.32,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 因為星野同學一直用宮姐這個稱呼 我一不小心…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:42.11,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,宮姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:43.80,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人就是傳聞中的宮姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.12,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,是小日向姐姐的那個宮姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:47.82,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,出來了好多小學生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.80,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:53.17,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,像剛才說好的一樣 在大姐姐面前排成一隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.37,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好 一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:17:01.53,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,宮姐小姐 謝謝你幫忙製作戲劇的服裝！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.56,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.00,0:17:11.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我先 聽說下次你要演電影 是哪部電影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:14.12,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我來 聽說你朋友上千是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:17.66,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是海歸子女並畢業于國外大學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.91,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是飛機的駕駛員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:24.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺中傳聞又變得更加離譜了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:28.51,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近很期待傳聞到底能變得多離譜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.86,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,請…請和我握手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:33.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.33,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:37.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我也想握手 等等我也想 我也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.38,0:17:40.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊 宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.65,0:17:42.05,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好好 大家排好隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.25,0:17:43.24,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,排好隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.30,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,一人十秒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.11,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的別插隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.13,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,松本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.55,0:17:51.71,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,松本也幫我們做衣服了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:52.83,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:58.75,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉尚未招呼你 這次真的很感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:03.16,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 我也只是幫宮子同學打打下手罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:05.79,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐是宮姐的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:07.57,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.84,0:18:09.84,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,算是她的摯友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.14,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.24,0:18:13.77,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,請下一位上前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:14.85,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,請上前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:18.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐貌似快到極限了 我們得去救她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:20.65,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:25.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,小日向因為宮姐姐很受歡迎 所以一時欣喜沒注意到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:26.89,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.80,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,感到困擾的話 就讓我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.13,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼好點子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:35.28,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.60,0:18:37.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那你為什麼站出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:39.89,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏音有什麼好的想法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.75,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:48.66,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,說著這是個整蠱 其實我不是宮姐姐 什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.25,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這個確實還是有點勉強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.36,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有一點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:56.70,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,夏音開玩笑的水準還是一如既往地差勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:59.32,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,啊原來是玩笑啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:02.15,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,因為沒想到夏音居然會開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:05.11,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在一起聊什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:07.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,宮姐姐救援計畫…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.36,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,宮姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:11.12,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,說是要去趟洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:14.50,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,逃走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.89,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我們分頭去找她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.26,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,夏音 我們也去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.36,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,宮姐姐 很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.20,0:19:27.53,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你不覺得她好像比想像中的更不起眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:31.16,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣 衣服和髮型什麼的 確實很不起眼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.48,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,你們真是不懂行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:36.60,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那些都是為了消除氣場的變裝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.33,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那些明星都會這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:39.91,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:43.10,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐 很受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:47.34,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我長大了會變得更加受人歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:51.63,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,比宮姐更上一層的話 小依想做偶像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.70,0:19:53.42,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒也不差
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:56.46,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我要成為被更多人尊敬的熱門人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.58,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,比偶像更進一步？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:00.51,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.49,0:20:03.65,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,是大總統哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.65,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是大總統啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:09.29,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.08,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:14.33,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真虧你能找到我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:17.79,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡沒有展出的裝飾 沒什麼人會過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:20.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,但說起來 你確實很努力了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:23.75,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,被班上的人包圍的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:25.60,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為你當下就會逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.39,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是有些長進的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然最後還是逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:35.01,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:38.22,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,開演前你那個樣子是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:41.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:42.80,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,人太多有點暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:48.42,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,因為平時也不會來這種人很多的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:50.72,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,你就那麼想看戲劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:53.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,因為 小花不僅是主角還是天使
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.55,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,日向和小乃愛也出場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:59.12,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,大家穿著我幫忙做的衣服 站在舞臺上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:01.33,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這是絕對不能錯過的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.30,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:08.10,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐你這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,平時比較怕生 有些畏畏縮縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:12.95,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,面對喜歡的事情 就會變得竭盡全力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:14.72,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,或者說是毫無顧忌了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:17.60,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:20.54,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一直在給小花添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.64,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是呢 還請你反省一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:28.75,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我覺得做事竭盡全力是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.60,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐拼命努力的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:35.27,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我不討厭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:39.74,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡癢癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:41.89,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,和那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:45.30,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次見到小花的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:47.46,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,胸口有癢癢的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:49.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,從那時候開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:51.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺中…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:58.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 閒聊到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.57,0:22:00.23,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,再加油一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:02.22,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:06.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,大家還在等著大姐姐從洗手間回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:09.56,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐姐不回去的話會很讓人困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.84,0:22:16.10,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那 就再努力一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺你比剛才精神些了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:20.31,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:22.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒什麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.84,0:22:26.65,TenshiOri_ddc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H242424&\frz270\pos(1556,368)}很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:30.82,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,結束了結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:32.32,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.57,0:22:33.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴 春香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:36.87,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,這之後叫上孩子們 一起辦慶功會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.07,0:22:37.95,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,慶功會？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:39.17,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:41.51,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那可以在我家舉辦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:43.94,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我就住你旁邊 沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:45.53,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:47.35,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:51.53,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟有個不在家舉辦就無法參加的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.95,0:22:58.90,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,說是之後要在我家舉辦慶功會 讓大家都過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:00.35,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:01.36,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:08.95,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,忘了去領印章卡兌換的零食了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:11.75,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,完全忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.71,0:23:15.71,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,那我來給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:18.40,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,到家我給你做你喜歡吃的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:19.82,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:21.45,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是宮姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:23.28,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}宮姐姐真溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.25,0:23:33.65,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,文化祭真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:38.30,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要和大家一起去大學的學園祭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:41.10,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,宮姐 我們一起進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.20,0:23:42.41,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,宮姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.45,0:23:43.19,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.70,0:23:43.50,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TenshiOri_txt,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:20.08,TenshiOri_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}さぁ 今夜も元気に始めましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:23.81,TenshiOri_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}天使が舞い降りる時間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:27.32,TenshiOri_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}自由気ままに　はしゃいで居たいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:30.66,TenshiOri_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一緒に遊びましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:36.20,TenshiOri_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}毎日色々とあるけど今日は！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:38.99,TenshiOri_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}全部ポイポイポイポイ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:45.54,TenshiOri_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}みんなで踊ろう両手を広げ　今
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:53.64,TenshiOri_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あなたのすぐそばにいるよ　気ままな天使たち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:23:01.20,TenshiOri_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨降り寂しいときには　笑顔で手をたたこう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:08.86,TenshiOri_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あなたのすぐそばにいるよ　辛いとき悲しいとき
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.04,0:23:16.46,TenshiOri_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}お星様キラキラ笑顔で　明日は晴れ模様
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:24.03,TenshiOri_EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}ドキドキはプレゼント ここだけの秘密だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:20.08,TenshiOri_EDCNtr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那麼 今晚也精神滿滿地開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:23.81,TenshiOri_EDCNtr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在天使降臨的時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:27.32,TenshiOri_EDCNtr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}隨心所欲地 開心快樂地在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:30.66,TenshiOri_EDCNtr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一起玩耍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:36.20,TenshiOri_EDCNtr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雖然每天都有各種事情但今天就
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.28,0:22:38.99,TenshiOri_EDCNtr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}全部忽視掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.24,0:22:45.54,TenshiOri_EDCNtr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}盡情享受張開雙手跳舞的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.12,0:22:53.64,TenshiOri_EDCNtr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}自由自在的天使們就在你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:23:01.20,TenshiOri_EDCNtr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}下雨寂寞難耐的時候 就笑著拍拍手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.36,0:23:08.86,TenshiOri_EDCNtr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}無論艱辛還是悲傷都會陪伴在你的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.04,0:23:16.46,TenshiOri_EDCNtr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}只要星星散發著閃爍的笑容 明天就會放晴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.86,0:23:24.03,TenshiOri_EDCNtr,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心跳的感覺就是禮物 這是僅屬於這裡的秘密
